  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Wash and dry the shallots. Cut them in half lengthwise.",
    "Place the shallot halves on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Drizzle each shallot half with olive oil, sprinkle smoked paprika, cumin, salt, and pepper evenly over them.",
    "Roast in the oven for about 20-25 minutes or until they become crispy on top and slightly softened inside.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro leaves before serving."
